name: Katherine Barrell
description:
Another request by @Zorglub! Katherine Barrell is an actress from Canada, best known for her role in Wynonna Earp.

The embed has been trained on SD 1.5 and works well on most 1.5 based models. On a few of the tested models such as Babes v20 there is a chance some birthmarks get overpronounced. Negative prompting or inpainting is recommended when this occurs, but it shouldn't happen too often.

If you enjoy my creations and want to support me or have a face you'd like to commission, consider supporting me on Ko-Fi or Buy Me A Coffee :)
